sentences.en: An inconspicuous urban underclass lives in squalor.
sentences.cn: 在这个肮脏破败的地方居住着不为人注意的城市下层阶级.

sentences.en: Even so, it was clear that Martin's earlier, inconspicuous life would never be the same again.
sentences.cn: 尽管如此, 马丁早期那种默默无闻的生活, 显然一去不复返了.

sentences.en: Fifth Elder Ma sits by himself in an inconspicuous corner drinking tea.
sentences.cn: 马五爷在不惹人注意的角落,独自坐着喝茶.

sentences.en: He had ridden out of Cambridge, inconspicuous among the hundreds of young cyclists.
sentences.cn: 他已骑车出了剑桥，淹没在几百名年轻的自行车手当中。

sentences.en: He was sidling into the bar, obviously trying to be inconspicuous.
sentences.cn: 他悄悄地走进酒吧，显然不想引起注意。

sentences.en: I am a seed, a very inconspicuous jujube tree seeds.
sentences.cn: 我是一粒种子, 一粒很不起眼的酸枣树的种子.

sentences.en: I'll try to be as inconspicuous as possible.
It was an ideally inconspicuous car for Keycase.
sentences.cn: 对奇开匙来说,这是一辆理想的不太显眼的汽车.

sentences.en: Low additional weight, unconstrained comfort, inconspicuous exterior.
sentences.cn: 低额外的重量, 不受约束的舒适, 不显眼的外观.

sentences.en: She stood by the wall, trying to look inconspicuous.
sentences.cn: 她贴墙站着，尽量不引人注目。

sentences.en: Test color - fastness and material compatibility in inconspicuous place before use. Do not over wet the carpet.
sentences.cn: 使用前在不显眼处测试不褪色性及材料相容性. 不要令地毯过湿.

sentences.en: Test in an inconspicuous area prior to first use.
The histology shows a dermal proliferation of small, irregular branching capillaries and venules with inconspicuous lumina.
sentences.cn: 组织学显示真皮内小 、 不规则分支状毛细血管和小静脉的增生,伴不明显的血管腔隙.

sentences.en: The newcomer tried to make herself as inconspicuous as possible , ie tried to avoid attention.
sentences.cn: 那个新来的人极力使她自己不惹人注意.

sentences.en: The shy girl tried to make herself as inconspicuous as possible.
sentences.cn: 那个怕羞的女孩子尽量使自己不被人注意.

sentences.en: Though wearied, she would be inconspicuous.
sentences.cn: 干活尽管累, 她可以避免自己的惹人注目.

words.tran_cn: 不显眼的；不引人注意的；（花）不显著的

trans.tran_cn: 不明显的，不显著的，不引人注目的
